gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Rockets 103, Spurs 101
gameRecap.excerpt: The Rockets defeated the Spurs, 103-101. Fred VanVleet put up 21 points, seven rebounds, seven assists and two steals for the Rockets, while Jalen Green added 16 points, seven rebounds and five assists in the victory. Tre Jones (24 points, five assists, three steals) and Jeremy Sochan (21 points, eight rebounds) combined for 45 points for the Spurs in the losing effort. The Rockets are on a three-game win streak as they improve to 30-35 on the season, while the Spurs fall to 14-52.
